# ğŸ“‹ REKAP FINAL LENGKAP - SITUNEO DIGITAL PLATFORM
## Complete Project Specification & Development Plan

**Project Name:** SITUNEO Digital Platform  
**Company:** PT Permata Cahaya Abadi  
**Director:** Devin Prasetyo Hermawan  
**Date:** November 9, 2025  
**Version:** 2.0 - Complete Rebuild (Fresh Start)

