### **1.4 Tugas Tambahan System (Job Board)**

#### **Flow Tugas dari Admin ke Partner**

```
1. ADMIN POST TUGAS
   â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”
   â”‚ Job Title: Bikin 10 Website E-Commerce â”‚
   â”‚ Deadline: 14 hari                  â”‚
   â”‚ Komisi: Rp 5,000,000              â”‚
   â”‚ Requirement: PHP, MySQL, WordPress â”‚
   â”‚ Description: [Detail lengkap...]   â”‚
   â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜
                  â”‚
                  â–¼
2. BROADCAST KE SEMUA PARTNER DASHBOARD
   - Notification muncul di dashboard partner
   - Email notif ke semua partner
   - WhatsApp notif (optional)
                  â”‚
                  â–¼
3. PARTNER KLIK "MINAT"
   - Partner A klik: "Saya Minat!"
   - Auto-confirm ke admin
   - Job status: "Pending Approval"
                  â”‚
                  â–¼
4. ADMIN APPROVE PARTNER
   - Admin review partner profile
   - Admin approve Partner A
   - Job status: "In Progress"
   - Deadline mulai hitung
                  â”‚
                  â–¼
5. PARTNER KERJA & SUBMIT
   - Partner upload hasil kerja
   - Partner submit ke admin
   - Job status: "Submitted"
                  â”‚
                  â–¼
6. ADMIN REVIEW & APPROVE
   - Admin cek kualitas
   - Admin approve â†’ Komisi masuk saldo partner
   - Admin reject â†’ Partner revisi
                  â”‚
                  â–¼
7. PENALTY SYSTEM (Jika Telat)
   - Telat 1-3 hari: Warning
   - Telat 4-7 hari: -10% komisi
   - Telat >7 hari: -25% komisi + Warning keras
   - Banyak telat: Partner blacklist dari job board
```

#### **Multi-Partner Jobs**
```
Jika job besar butuh >1 partner:
âœ… Admin set: "Need 3 partners"
âœ… Partner apply, admin pilih 3 terbaik
âœ… Komisi dibagi sesuai kontribusi:
   - Lead partner: 50%
   - Support 1: 25%
   - Support 2: 25%
   
Atau admin yang tentuin pembagian custom
```

