## ğŸ“± **5. RESPONSIVE DESIGN**

### **5.1 Breakpoints**

```css
/* Mobile First Approach */
--breakpoint-xs: 0px;      /* Extra small devices */
--breakpoint-sm: 576px;    /* Small devices (landscape phones) */
--breakpoint-md: 768px;    /* Medium devices (tablets) */
--breakpoint-lg: 992px;    /* Large devices (desktops) */
--breakpoint-xl: 1200px;   /* Extra large devices (large desktops) */
--breakpoint-xxl: 1400px;  /* Extra extra large devices */
```

### **5.2 Mobile Priority**

```
FOKUS UTAMA: Mobile (320px - 768px)
- Perfect UX di HP
- Touch-friendly (min 44px tap targets)
- Optimized loading untuk mobile data
- Mobile-first navigation

DESKTOP: Responsive (768px+)
- Secukupnya (tidak perlu fancy desktop-exclusive)
- Multi-column layouts
- Hover effects
- Keyboard navigation
```

### **5.3 Testing Devices Priority**

```
1. Android Chrome (HIGHEST PRIORITY)
   - Samsung Galaxy (berbagai ukuran)
   - Xiaomi
   - Oppo, Vivo
   
2. iPhone Safari
   - iPhone 12/13/14/15
   - Various screen sizes

3. Tablet
   - iPad
   - Android tablets

4. Desktop
   - 1920Ã—1080 (Full HD)
   - 1366Ã—768 (Laptop)
```

