## âœ… **11. QUALITY STANDARDS**

### **11.1 Code Quality**

```
âœ… Clean Code
   - Readable variable names
   - Proper indentation
   - Comments where necessary
   - No duplicate code (DRY principle)

âœ… File Organization
   - 1 file = 1 purpose
   - Max ~200 lines per file
   - Clear folder structure
   - Meaningful file names (orang bodoh pun paham)

âœ… Documentation
   - Header comments per file:
     /**
      * File: filename.php
      * Purpose: What this file does
      * Author: [Your name]
      * Date: YYYY-MM-DD
      */
   
   - Function comments:
     /**
      * Function description
      * @param type $param Description
      * @return type Description
      */

âœ… Error Handling
   - Try-catch blocks
   - Meaningful error messages
   - Log errors properly
   - Never expose sensitive info

âœ… Security
   - Input validation everywhere
   - SQL injection prevention
   - XSS prevention
   - CSRF protection
```

### **11.2 Design Quality**

```
âœ… Visual Hierarchy
   - Clear heading structure (H1 â†’ H6)
   - Proper spacing
   - Consistent typography
   - Color contrast (WCAG AA minimum)

âœ… User Experience
   - Intuitive navigation
   - Clear CTAs
   - Helpful error messages
   - Loading indicators
   - Success feedback

âœ… Responsiveness
   - Mobile-first design
   - Breakpoint testing
   - Touch-friendly (44px min)
   - No horizontal scroll

âœ… Performance
   - Optimized images
   - Lazy loading
   - Minified assets
   - Caching headers

âœ… Accessibility
   - Alt text for images
   - ARIA labels where needed
   - Keyboard navigation
   - Screen reader friendly
```

